    "## 問題"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "add_taxを追加してください。このメソッド内で、ユーザーの入力値に8%を加算してください。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 解答"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 4,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
      "text/plain": [
       "108"
      ]
     },
     "execution_count": 4,
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "execute_result"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "def add_tax(input)\n",
    "  input *= 1.08\n",
    "  return input.round()\n",
    "end\n",
    "\n",
    "add_tax(100)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
